title: FSU student Maura Binkley gunned down in "HOT YOGA CLASS" by INCEL Perv
itunes:title: FSU student Maura Binkley gunned down in "HOT YOGA CLASS" by INCEL Perv
description:
Two shot and killed, four wounded, one pistol whipped... all at the hands of a self proclaimed "incel." Today, Nancy Grace and her guests take a deep look at the subculture of "involuntary celebate, " and its link to an increase in assaults on women. Our focus is a gunman's brutal attack on a Florida hot yoga studio. Joining our panel, Jeff Binkley, founder of Maura's Voice. His daughter Maura was one of those killed. Also with us: Washington Post Opinion Columnist Christine Emba, Prosecutor Wendy Patrick, Former NYPD John Cardillo, and Psychoanalyst Dr. Bethany Marshall.
